# .clauderc - Claude Code Instructions

# Project Overview
This file contains instructions for Claude when exploring this project.

# Project Context
i. This project uses python and manim.
ii. Read the design documentation: "claude explore design.md"
iii. Read the claude generated README: "claude explore README.md"

# File Patterns to Explore
# Note: When using this file, ask Claude to:
- Read all markdown documentation: "claude explore *.md"
- Read source code: "claude explore *.py"
- Read input files: "claude explore sim*.json"

# Common Tasks
1. Follow existing naming conventions
2. Update README.md documentation when adding or changing features.

# Explore commands to individually copy and paste at the claude prompt.
claude explore .clauderc design.md README.md
claude explore *.py sim*.json